{"tid":613006,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/Xbox]盜賊之海 Sea of Thieves","createTime":"2018-04-01T09:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T11:52:23.000Z","uid":16488,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"92773991165e8fb39136c11883cee7fa1d52a59e","tid":613006,"uid":16488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/173450_9a72c6f436929d23db68e2742bdac226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F173450_9a72c6f436929d23db68e2742bdac226.jpg&h=816d840d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《盜賊之海》是款非常強調自由度的遊戲，玩家可以在這片大海上扮演心目中的海盜，與三五好友一起建造海盜船出航。過程中玩家可以自行選擇想要扮演的角色，如操控船隻前進方向的航海士、鼓舞船員士氣的樂手或是操控大砲的戰鬥人員。<br />\n <br />\n在實際的遊戲過程中，由於所有的船員都是由真人玩家組成，因此在戰鬥時往往會亂成一團，大家七嘴八舌地指揮要往哪個方向轉彎才能躲避敵艦的炮擊，若是船隻受損還得前往船艙修理才不會進水沉沒。儘管如此，同心協力進行的遊戲過程充滿樂趣，即使船隻不幸沉沒，也可以在現場的試玩機台旁聽到外國玩家彼此揶揄的笑聲。(轉自巴哈)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r5JIBaasuE8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr5JIBaasuE8&d=qAUHm39efqk3lQPpkVvpYKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=6160d3ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r5JIBaasuE8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">PC版一定要Win10</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPC買Game渠道 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/store/productId/9P2N57MC619K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fstore%2FproductId%2F9P2N57MC619K&d=qAUHm39efqk3lQPpkVvpYKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=31c9a8e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/store/productId/9P2N57MC619K</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Discord 暫時有11位巴打，一晚都有一兩隊船出到</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/TzG4BgF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FTzG4BgF&d=qAUHm39efqk3lQPpkVvpYKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=4c4a327e\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/TzG4BgF</a><br />\n<br />\n官網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.seaofthieves.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seaofthieves.com%2F&d=qAUHm39efqk3lQPpkVvpYKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=147acbd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.seaofthieves.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時遊戲有三種等級，等級只同可接任務相關，與能力無關。<br />\n<br />\n三種分別係   <br />\nGold Hoarders 尋寶解迷<br />\nMerchant Alliance  交易送貨同捉動物<br />\nOrder of Souls  打怪獵頭<br />\n<br />\n三種都可以賺到錢，交任愈多升得愈高。亦會升聲望，聲望到某個位會成為傳說海盜，會有隻傳說船同有新任務。<br />\n<br />\n武器方面有刀、手槍、散彈同狙擊。槍類只有5發子彈，用晒要搵子彈箱reload(船上必有，島上亦可能有)。"},{"pid":"7d7667681a1efb584cd49220e9f9cebca39ad671","tid":613006,"uid":16488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faa58ed3d02e9b73e1178daa07703d21484acdd","tid":613006,"uid":37343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:14:40.000Z","msg":"刺激感麻麻。申xboxonex"},{"pid":"3e0dee59851b16c80c3f3079dc97ce03a9a98488","tid":613006,"uid":48016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"賣寶箱得百幾蚊, D裝成皮野, 挖到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1907db26182b18574d4af29da957df444a457018","tid":613006,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"Twitch 好似都幾多人玩下<br />\n<br />\nBtw繼pubg之後又一隻正game冇ps4份"},{"pid":"1ce638c9fa27f977998af9ab3cc6bf8cddf4ed42","tid":613006,"uid":147001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"好似幾好玩, 但我怕我部虧機捱唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71ceeb7d01789004300ca8ae9f492fea2394b92","tid":613006,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1907db26182b18574d4af29da957df444a457018","tid":613006,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"Twitch 好似都幾多人玩下<br />\